OL,3,CBBC News to restructure Singapore
OL,4,Coperation
OL,6,GStaff at BBC News have today been
OL,7,Ginformed of changes planned for the
OL,8,GSingapore operation.
OL,10,FMost of the editorial team based in
OL,11,FSingapore come under the Money and
OL,12,FWork team and provide news and
OL,13,Fbusiness coverage for the BBC News
OL,14,Fchannel, from 2am until 5am.
OL,16,FThe new plan for Singapore will see
OL,17,Fthe creation of seven new roles: a
OL,18,Fnews editor, five senior journalists
OL,19,Fand one journalist. These roles will
OL,20,Fcome under news channel line
OL,21,Fmanagement and will be advertised
OL,22,Finternally and externally.
