OL,6,FThe existing Money and Work team will
OL,7,Fbe scaled back significantly ` with
OL,8,Fall senior journalist roles being
OL,9,Fclosed ` with a new focus on "high
OL,10,Fimpact, multi-platform stories".
OL,12,FThe new roles will be advertised soon,
OL,13,Fwith recruitment expected to be
OL,14,Fcomplete by early March.
OL,16,FThe changes will bring Singapore more
OL,17,Finto line with operations in London
OL,18,Fand Washington DC. Singapore will also
OL,19,Fassume technical autonomy, allowing it
OL,20,Fto operate independently of London.
