OL,6,FIn the communication to staff, BBC
OL,7,FNews channel executive news editor,
OL,8,FPaul Royall said the change "allows us
OL,9,Fto deepen the BBC's 'Follow the Sun'
OL,10,Feditorial strategy, with channel teams
OL,11,Fworking closely with digital
OL,12,Fcolleagues and delivering live news 24/
OL,13,F7 from London, DC, and Singapore."
